<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main>
  <section class="rule-b">
    <div class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pt-16 sm:pt-24 pb-16 sm:pb-20 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-8">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-2">
        <span class="kicker kicker-rule">§ The Lab</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-10">
        <p class="font-mono text-[0.8rem] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-4 mb-8">Ljubljana · Slovenia · European Union</p>
        <h1 class="display-xl text-balance">A small lab,<br><span class="font-display-italic">a long supply chain.</span></h1>
        <p class="mt-10 lede max-w-prose">Helix Research is a research-supply distributor based in Ljubljana, Slovenia. We source from cGMP-audited European peptide CMOs, run incoming-lot QC against our release specification, and ship every parcel from our own fulfilment hub in the EU. Everything you order touches three sets of hands before it reaches your bench, and every step is documented.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-10">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-2">
        <span class="kicker kicker-rule">§ Origin</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-10">
        <h2 class="display-lg text-balance">Why <span class="font-display-italic">Ljubljana.</span></h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-10 mt-12">
          <div>
            <p class="text-[1.05rem] text-ink-2 leading-[1.75]">Slovenia has been making pharmaceuticals since 1946. The Lek line — now part of the Novartis group through Sandoz — sits a short drive from our facility, and several generations of process chemists trained inside that programme are now scattered across the country's biotech sector.</p>
            <p class="text-[1.05rem] text-ink-2 leading-[1.75] mt-5">When we set up Helix in 2022, the technical labour pool we needed — peptide chemists, lyophilisation operators, QC analysts who can read an LC-MS spectrum without a textbook open beside them — already existed within twenty kilometres of the office.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-[1.05rem] text-ink-2 leading-[1.75]">The geography helped too. Ljubljana sits at the crossing of three transit corridors: the Alps to Munich and Vienna, the Adriatic to Trieste and Venice, and the Pannonian basin to Budapest and Bratislava. EU couriers reach the major Western European destinations from us in 2 to 3 working days. Eastern European destinations land in 3 to 5.</p>
            <p class="text-[1.05rem] text-ink-2 leading-[1.75] mt-5">And the regulatory environment is the boring kind, which is the kind we want. Slovenian medicines law sits cleanly inside the EU framework. There is no national exception, no legal grey zone, no special carve-out we have to navigate.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper-2 rule-y">
    <div class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-10">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-2">
        <span class="kicker kicker-rule">§ Facility</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-10">
        <h2 class="display-lg text-balance">The <span class="font-display-italic">facility.</span></h2>
        <p class="mt-8 lede max-w-prose">Roughly 1,400 m² across two floors in the BTC business park east of the city centre. We share the building with two other life-sciences tenants and a contract logistics operator. Nothing on the exterior signage mentions peptides, chemistry, or research supply — for the same plain-professional reasons we apply to outbound parcels.</p>

        <dl class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-rule border-block border-rule">
          <div class="bg-bg p-7">
            <dt class="kicker mb-3">Footprint</dt>
            <dd class="display-sm">1,400 m²</dd>
            <dd class="text-[0.9rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Across QC laboratory, controlled-temperature storage, lyo-stable inventory, and fulfilment.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg p-7">
            <dt class="kicker mb-3">Storage</dt>
            <dd class="display-sm">−20 / +5 / +20 °C</dd>
            <dd class="text-[0.9rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Three temperature-mapped rooms with continuous logging and out-of-spec alerting.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg p-7">
            <dt class="kicker mb-3">QC instruments</dt>
            <dd class="display-sm">HPLC + LC-MS</dd>
            <dd class="text-[0.9rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Agilent 1260 Infinity II analytical HPLC; LC-MS via Shimadzu LCMS-2050. Routine identity and re-test.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg p-7">
            <dt class="kicker mb-3">Throughput</dt>
            <dd class="display-sm">~3,200 lots / yr</dd>
            <dd class="text-[0.9rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Across 49 SKUs and the full release-and-fulfilment workflow.</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-10">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-2">
        <span class="kicker kicker-rule">§ Supply</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-10">
        <h2 class="display-lg text-balance">Where the <span class="font-display-italic">molecules come from.</span></h2>
        <p class="mt-8 lede max-w-prose">We do not synthesise from raw resin in-house. Helix is a research-supply distributor; the synthesis is done by partner CMOs that operate at a scale and audit posture we could not justify replicating at our throughput.</p>

        <ol class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1">
          <% [
            ['01', 'Synthesis', 'Two cGMP-audited contract manufacturers in Switzerland and Italy handle the bulk of the catalogue. Both operate under EU GMP and have been audited by their national competent authorities. We sign supply agreements that include batch-record continuity, raw-material traceability, and right-to-audit clauses.'],
            ['02', 'Inbound QC', 'Every incoming lot is sampled and re-tested at our Ljubljana QC lab against our release specification: HPLC purity ≥ 98% by area, LC-MS identity within 0.1 Da of theoretical, sterility per USP <71>, endotoxin via LAL kinetic-chromogenic assay, water content by Karl Fischer.'],
            ['03', 'Lot release', 'Lots that meet specification are released into saleable inventory and assigned a Helix lot number that traces back to the manufacturer batch. The Helix COA is generated and stored against the lot.'],
            ['04', 'Storage', 'Released inventory is held at the appropriate temperature for the compound — typically −20 °C lyophilised. Storage rooms are temperature-mapped and continuously logged.'],
            ['05', 'Fulfilment', 'Orders are picked, packed in cold-chain insulated mailers with phase-change inserts, and dispatched from our fulfilment area to a tracked EU courier. The COA travels with the parcel.'],
          ].forEach((step) => { %>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[64px_1fr] gap-x-6 py-7 rule-t">
              <span class="font-mono text-[0.78rem] text-ink-5 pt-1.5"><%= step[0] %></span>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[180px_1fr] gap-x-8 gap-y-2">
                <p class="font-display text-[1.3rem] font-medium leading-snug"><%= step[1] %></p>
                <p class="text-[0.95rem] text-ink-3 leading-relaxed max-w-prose"><%= step[2] %></p>
              </div>
            </li>
          <% }) %>
          <li class="rule-t"></li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper-2 rule-y">
    <div class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-10">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-2">
        <span class="kicker kicker-rule">§ People</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-10">
        <h2 class="display-lg text-balance">A small team, <span class="font-display-italic">technical from end to end.</span></h2>
        <p class="mt-8 lede max-w-prose">Eleven people in Ljubljana, no marketing department, no sales team. Everyone we hire has a benchwork background — peptide chemistry, analytical chemistry, or pharmaceutical QC — because the work requires it.</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 mt-14">
          <article class="rule-t pt-6">
            <span class="kicker text-cobalt mb-2 inline-block">Founders</span>
            <p class="font-display text-[1.15rem] font-medium leading-snug">Two analytical chemists</p>
            <p class="text-[0.92rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">PhDs in peptide chemistry, both with prior QC roles inside EU pharmaceutical generics. Helix is their second company.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="rule-t pt-6">
            <span class="kicker text-cobalt mb-2 inline-block">QC team</span>
            <p class="font-display text-[1.15rem] font-medium leading-snug">Four analysts</p>
            <p class="text-[0.92rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">HPLC, LC-MS, sterility, endotoxin. Combined ~40 years of regulated-environment QC experience.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="rule-t pt-6">
            <span class="kicker text-cobalt mb-2 inline-block">Operations</span>
            <p class="font-display text-[1.15rem] font-medium leading-snug">Three operators</p>
            <p class="text-[0.92rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Inbound receiving, controlled-temperature storage, outbound packing, courier handoff. ISO 9001-aligned SOPs.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="rule-t pt-6">
            <span class="kicker text-cobalt mb-2 inline-block">Customer technical</span>
            <p class="font-display text-[1.15rem] font-medium leading-snug">Two researchers</p>
            <p class="text-[0.92rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">MSc-level scientists who answer COA, batch-record, and protocol-design questions from researchers. They reply, not a script.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="rule-t pt-6">
            <span class="kicker text-cobalt mb-2 inline-block">Compliance</span>
            <p class="font-display text-[1.15rem] font-medium leading-snug">External counsel</p>
            <p class="text-[0.92rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">EU-qualified pharmaceutical lawyer reviewing operations, supply agreements, and customer-facing documentation.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="rule-t pt-6">
            <span class="kicker text-cobalt mb-2 inline-block">Audit posture</span>
            <p class="font-display text-[1.15rem] font-medium leading-snug">ISO 9001 in flight</p>
            <p class="text-[0.92rem] text-ink-3 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Quality management system documented; certification audit scheduled for late 2026. Internal audit reports available on request.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 grid grid-cols-12 gap-6">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7">
        <span class="kicker kicker-rule mb-4 inline-flex">§ Posture</span>
        <h2 class="display-lg mt-3 text-balance">A research supplier, <span class="font-display-italic">not a pharmacy.</span></h2>
        <p class="mt-7 lede max-w-prose">Helix sits in the research-supply layer of the EU peptide ecosystem. We sell research-grade compounds for in-vitro and laboratory work, with batch documentation and a clear audit trail. We do not operate as a pharmacy, do not dispense prescription medicines, and do not market for human or animal consumption. The line is the line. Sitting cleanly inside it is what makes us a five-year business instead of a six-month one.</p>
        <p class="mt-7 lede max-w-prose">Read more about how this maps to the broader EU ecosystem in <a href="/blog/eu-research-supply-ecosystem" class="link-underline">our Journal article on the European peptide research-supply ecosystem</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-3 lg:items-end lg:justify-end">
        <a href="/quality" class="btn btn-primary">See the QC pipeline →</a>
        <a href="/shipping" class="btn btn-secondary">See the logistics →</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost">Get in touch →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/cart-drawer') %>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
<%- include('partials/scripts') %>
